#. Plugin URI of the plugin
msgid "https://github.com/guilamu/gf-advanced-conditional-choices"
msgstr "https://github.com/guilamu/gf-advanced-conditional-choices"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"Add conditional logic to individual choices in Radio, Checkbox, Dropdown, "
"and Multi-Select fields."
msgstr ""
"Ajoute une logique conditionnelle aux choix individuels dans les champs "
"Boutons radio, Cases à cocher, Liste déroulante et Sélection multiple."

#. Author of the plugin
msgid "Guilamu"
msgstr "Guilamu"

